  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/1c9ed3c3495657e846f6f60c5a41329e.poster.avif?t=1665146809\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/1c9ed3c3495657e846f6f60c5a41329e.webm?t=1665146809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/1c9ed3c3495657e846f6f60c5a41329e.mp4?t=1665146809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/5630d81e85d72b2041a8ffdc6998233c.webp?t=1665146809\" width=620 height=22 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/9b162f3ca082cd5ab76f8919ac484c65.avif?t=1665146809\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br>Glyph is \"hard as nails,\" pure and old-school platforming in modern dress. You don't level up or get bonuses; you get further by getting better. This game is all about the controls and the environment. Use both in combination to progress and do it at your own pace. <br><br>For inspiration, tips and tricks, fresh content, competitions, and community visit the Glyph Discord server: <br><br>Have fun! And see you there.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The list:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Time trials<br></li><li>Pure platforming<br></li><li>Refine your skill<br></li><li>Original soundtrack<br></li><li>Customizable cosmetics<br></li><li>Explore and solve puzzles<br></li><li>Value for money at 80+ levels<br></li><li>Route planning in open worlds<br></li><li>One-of-a-kind abilities and controls</li></ul>⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<strong><i>Glyph: Easy to leap, difficult to land!</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/5630d81e85d72b2041a8ffdc6998233c.webp?t=1665146809\" width=620 height=22 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/c515ca31df8cc00222bd120ac2436dad.poster.avif?t=1665146809\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/c515ca31df8cc00222bd120ac2436dad.webm?t=1665146809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/c515ca31df8cc00222bd120ac2436dad.mp4?t=1665146809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/5630d81e85d72b2041a8ffdc6998233c.webp?t=1665146809\" width=620 height=22 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/3e2979ca6db936c63302ad201ec584dd.avif?t=1665146809\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><i> “Glyph gives you a deep-felt sense of achievement.”<br><br>“Thoughtful. Magical. It’s the kind of game they don’t make anymore.”<br><br>“You will feel calm, challenged, and entirely swept away to a distant land. “<br><br>“The soundtrack? It’s mesmerizing.”</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/5630d81e85d72b2041a8ffdc6998233c.webp?t=1665146809\" width=620 height=22 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/301897d799f5bfb3654546834238fe6f.poster.avif?t=1665146809\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/301897d799f5bfb3654546834238fe6f.webm?t=1665146809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/301897d799f5bfb3654546834238fe6f.mp4?t=1665146809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/5630d81e85d72b2041a8ffdc6998233c.webp?t=1665146809\" width=620 height=22 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/beb208db97c833ad23e4a2b5f79c56e1.avif?t=1665146809\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Glyph is perfect for speedrunning, but all of the beautiful 80+ levels contain secrets for you to uncover - if you can find them.<br><br>That means the adventurous gamer has plenty of things to discover.<br><br>And for those who crave adrenaline, Glyph offers 30 heart-thumping, controller-clenching time trials pushing you to develop your skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/5630d81e85d72b2041a8ffdc6998233c.webp?t=1665146809\" width=620 height=22 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/71d3fcd99ac2c71a8ffaf2fa79bb43c2.poster.avif?t=1665146809\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/71d3fcd99ac2c71a8ffaf2fa79bb43c2.webm?t=1665146809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569150/extras/71d3fcd99ac2c71a8ffa